2014-03-14 17:51:12	--	- ORWELL, GEORGE [1903 - 1950] Born in India, his mother
2014-03-14 17:51:12	--	- moved him to England when he was one year old, and it
2014-03-14 17:51:12	--	- was in England where he was educated and spent most of
2014-03-14 17:51:12	--	- his life.  Orwell is perhaps best known for his novels
2014-03-14 17:51:12	--	- Nineteen Eighty-Four and Animal Farm.
