2014-03-14 17:51:12	--	- volunteer staff and helpful users will be happy to assist you.
2014-03-14 17:51:12	--	-
2014-03-14 17:51:12	--	- You can meet us at FOSSCON (http://www.fosscon.org) where we get
2014-03-14 17:51:12	--	- together with like-minded FOSS enthusiasts for talks and
2014-03-14 17:51:12	--	- real-life collaboration, if you're more keen on the outdoors why
2014-03-14 17:51:12	--	- not attend or arrange a local geeknic (http://www.geeknic.org).
