2014-03-14 20:13:07	--	- orwell.freenode.net Message of the Day -
2014-03-14 20:13:07	--	- Welcome to orwell.freenode.net in Amsterdam, NL.
2014-03-14 20:13:07	--	- Thanks to http://www.hyperfilter.com/ for sponsoring
2014-03-14 20:13:07	--	- this server!
2014-03-14 20:13:07	--	-
2014-03-14 20:13:07	--	- ORWELL, GEORGE [1903 - 1950] Born in India, his mother
2014-03-14 20:13:07	--	- moved him to England when he was one year old, and it
2014-03-14 20:13:07	--	- was in England where he was educated and spent most of
2014-03-14 20:13:07	--	- his life.  Orwell is perhaps best known for his novels
2014-03-14 20:13:07	--	- Nineteen Eighty-Four and Animal Farm.
2014-03-14 20:13:07	--	-
2014-03-14 20:13:07	--	-
2014-03-14 20:13:07	--	- Welcome to freenode - supporting the free and open source
2014-03-14 20:13:07	--	- software communities since 1998.
2014-03-14 20:13:07	--	-
2014-03-14 20:13:07	--	- By connecting to freenode you indicate that you have read and
2014-03-14 20:13:07	--	- accept our policies as set out on http://www.freenode.net
2014-03-14 20:13:07	--	- freenode runs an open proxy scanner. Please join #freenode for
2014-03-14 20:13:07	--	- any network-related questions or queries, where a number of
2014-03-14 20:13:07	--	- volunteer staff and helpful users will be happy to assist you.
2014-03-14 20:13:07	--	-
2014-03-14 20:13:07	--	- You can meet us at FOSSCON (http://www.fosscon.org) where we get
2014-03-14 20:13:07	--	- together with like-minded FOSS enthusiasts for talks and
2014-03-14 20:13:07	--	- real-life collaboration, if you're more keen on the outdoors why
2014-03-14 20:13:07	--	- not attend or arrange a local geeknic (http://www.geeknic.org).
2014-03-14 20:13:07	--	-
2014-03-14 20:13:07	--	- We would like to thank Private Internet Access
2014-03-14 20:13:07	--	- (https://www.privateinternetaccess.com/) and the other
2014-03-14 20:13:07	--	- organisations that help keep freenode and our other projects
2014-03-14 20:13:07	--	- running for their sustained support.
2014-03-14 20:13:07	--	-
2014-03-14 20:13:07	--	- In particular we would like to thank the sponsor
2014-03-14 20:13:07	--	- of this server, details of which can be found above.
2014-03-14 20:13:07	--	-
2014-03-14 20:13:07	--	- ***************************************************************
2014-03-14 20:13:07	--	- Please read http://blog.freenode.net/2010/11/be-safe-out-there/
2014-03-14 20:13:07	--	- ***************************************************************
