2014-03-16 16:23:01	--	- rajaniemi.freenode.net Message of the Day -
2014-03-16 16:23:01	--	- Welcome to rajaniemi.freenode.net in Helsinki, Finland.  Our thanks to
2014-03-16 16:23:01	--	- Aalto University for sponsoring this server!
2014-03-16 16:23:01	--	-
2014-03-16 16:23:01	--	- RAJANIEMI, Hannu  (1978-). Born in Ylivieska, Finland, Rajaniemi is the
2014-03-16 16:23:01	--	- author of two novels and several short stories, and his debut novel 'The
2014-03-16 16:23:01	--	- Quantum Thief' was nominated for the 2011 Locus Award for Best First
2014-03-16 16:23:01	--	- Novel.  Rajaniemi lives in Edinburgh, Scotland where he is founding
2014-03-16 16:23:01	--	- director of ThinkTank Maths, a commercial research
2014-03-16 16:23:01	--	-
2014-03-16 16:23:01	--	-
2014-03-16 16:23:01	--	- Welcome to freenode - supporting the free and open source
2014-03-16 16:23:01	--	- software communities since 1998.
2014-03-16 16:23:01	--	-
2014-03-16 16:23:01	--	- By connecting to freenode you indicate that you have read and
2014-03-16 16:23:01	--	- accept our policies as set out on http://www.freenode.net
2014-03-16 16:23:01	--	- freenode runs an open proxy scanner. Please join #freenode for
2014-03-16 16:23:01	--	- any network-related questions or queries, where a number of
2014-03-16 16:23:01	--	- volunteer staff and helpful users will be happy to assist you.
2014-03-16 16:23:01	--	-
2014-03-16 16:23:01	--	- You can meet us at FOSSCON (http://www.fosscon.org) where we get
2014-03-16 16:23:01	--	- together with like-minded FOSS enthusiasts for talks and
2014-03-16 16:23:01	--	- real-life collaboration, if you're more keen on the outdoors why
2014-03-16 16:23:01	--	- not attend or arrange a local geeknic (http://www.geeknic.org).
2014-03-16 16:23:01	--	-
2014-03-16 16:23:01	--	- We would like to thank Private Internet Access
2014-03-16 16:23:01	--	- (https://www.privateinternetaccess.com/) and the other
2014-03-16 16:23:01	--	- organisations that help keep freenode and our other projects
2014-03-16 16:23:01	--	- running for their sustained support.
2014-03-16 16:23:01	--	-
2014-03-16 16:23:01	--	- In particular we would like to thank the sponsor
2014-03-16 16:23:01	--	- of this server, details of which can be found above.
